Digital Health Solution Platform 
Senior Test Engineer 
• Project Description: The platform provides an infrastructure for data collection from broad sources including 
genomics, environment, lifestyle, behaviours and electronic health records. 
• Main duties:  
o Join a new scrum team as a senior test engineer and engage in all scrum events. 
o Coaching new team members about product domain, testing techniques, working processes, and other 
collaboration matters. 
o Engage with other team members on implementing and testing the new tickets. 
o Collaborate with other teams and product owner on requirements and develop test case and test strategy. 
o Plan and execute the test for new features. 
o Reporting bug by using Jira system.  
o E2E testing, API testing using Postman.
